{"data": [{"id": "4742170", "title": "Of Three Apple Suppliers, Only Skyworks Solutions Hit Street Guidance", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wide shot of batter hitting pitch during professional baseball game\" data-id=\"1492416305\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Skyworks Solutions (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SWKS\" title=\"Skyworks Solutions, Inc.\">SWKS</a></span>) was the only one of three Apple mixed signal suppliers to come close at hitting analysts targets. This is the third of three articles profiling Cirrus Logic (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRUS\" title=\"Cirrus Logic, Inc.\">CRUS</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1492416305/image_1492416305.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742170-of-three-apple-suppliers-only-skyworks-solutions-hit-street-guidance", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 02:20:34"}, {"id": "4742168", "title": "BRRR: Bitcoin's Dominance Is Slipping", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Crypto currency and digital wallets concept background. Futuristic bitcoin icon in world of technological progress and innovation. CGI 3D render\" data-id=\"2149225006\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>After a four-month rally, the market has taken Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) from a low of $49k in early August up to $99.7k in late November. An epic tease, perhaps. With many, myself included, expecting a $100k BTC price, crypto's top coin is taking a breather. Have we already</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742168-brrr-bitcoins-dominance-is-slipping", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 02:12:44"}, {"id": "4742183", "title": "Ooma, Inc. 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Ooma, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106027\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742183-ooma-inc-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 02:06:20"}, {"id": "4742181", "title": "AeroVironment, Inc. 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by AeroVironment, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106026\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742181-aerovironment-inc-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 01:58:48"}, {"id": "4742163", "title": "SCHD: Wall Street Analysts Are Bullish And So Am I (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads