cember finds only Verizon (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VZ\" title=\"Verizon Communications Inc.\">VZ</a>), living up to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/149130950/image_149130950.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742161-dow-30-december-dogs-show-28-pay-dividends-and-1-safer-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 01:37:18"}, {"id": "4742160", "title": "Is AT&T Becoming A Growth Stock?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Arlington\"s AT&amp;T Stadium' data-id=\"1283601718\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283601718/image_1283601718.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Art Wager/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figca