", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1770285634/image_1770285634.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742158-no-rocket-lab-stock-does-not-defy-gravity-technical-analysis", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 01:12:38"}, {"id": "4742156", "title": "British American Tobacco: New Glo Hilo Looks Like A Winner", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tabakh\u00e4ndler in Wien, \u00d6sterreich\" data-id=\"577303436\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">TasfotoNL/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Readers of my latest articles know that I 